ZH: 这些脏话简直是对公共场所的亵渎。
EN: These vulgar words are an utter profanity in public places.

ZH: 他亵渎了她的名誉，逼迫她辞去了工作。
EN: He defamed her honor and forced her to resign from her job.

ZH: 他的行为完全亵渎了这个庄严的教堂。
EN: His behavior completely profaned this solemn church.

